      • search

        @GET
 @Path(value="/{orgUuid}/search")
 @Produces(value="application/vnd.ilandcloud.api.v0.5+json")
SearchResult search(@PathParam(value="orgUuid")
                                                                                                                        String orgUuid,
                                                                                                                        @QueryParam(value="query")
                                                                                                                        String query,
                                                                                                                        @QueryParam(value="offset")
                                                                                                                        int offset,
                                                                                                                        @QueryParam(value="limit")
                                                                                                                        int limit)
        Perform a full-text search of entities pertaining to this organization.
        Parameters:
        orgUuid - organization uuid
        query - query string

        The query string accepts Lucene style query input.


        For example to search for networks with IPs in the 10.10.10.X subnet you would supply '10.10.10.*' as a query string. Tht * represents a wildcard character and can be used anywhere in a query EXCEPT for as the first character.


        To search for multiple terms that MUST occur the AND operator can be used. E.g. to find documents containing both 'network' and 'vapp' you would supply the query string 'network AND vapp' .

        offset - page offset for return documents
        limit - limit to number of hits (default value is 10 and maximum is 50)

      • updateDrsAffinityRules

        @PUT
 @Path(value="/{orgUuid}/drs-rules")
 @Produces(value="application/vnd.ilandcloud.api.v0.5+json")
 @Consumes(value="application/vnd.ilandcloud.api.v0.5+json")
CoreTask updateDrsAffinityRules(@PathParam(value="orgUuid")
                                                                                                                                                                                                    String orgUuid,
                                                                                                                                                                                                    List<VmAffinityRuleSpec> ruleSpecs)
        Update the DRS affinity and anti-affinity rules for the given organization. The rules can be of two types 'affinity' or 'anti-affinity' There are 3 operations that can be performed on the rules:
        • add
        • update
        • delete
        The update and delete operations require the rule uuid and key fields to be populated in order to perform rule update or rule deletion, respectively.
        Parameters:
        orgUuid - org uuid
        Returns:
        core task

      • getVpgsForOrg
